<span class="n">From:</span> <span class="o">&lt;&amp;</span><span class="n">from</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
<span class="n">To:</span> <span class="o">&lt;&amp;</span><span class="n">to</span><span class="o">&gt;</span>
<span class="n">Subject:</span> <span class="o">&lt;&amp;</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">さんにメッセージが届いています</span>

<span class="o">&lt;&amp;</span><span class="n">name</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">さんに</span><span class="o">&lt;&amp;</span><span class="n">fromname</span><span class="o">&gt;</span><span class="err">さんからメッセージが届いています。</span>
