<div class="comment" id="comment1483">
  <p class="banner"><a href="/web/20090523155028/http://ja.doukaku.org/user/235/" target="_top">onjo</a>

	
	&nbsp;
	<a href="/web/20090523155028/http://ja.doukaku.org/comment/1483/">#1483</a>(<script language="JavaScript">print_time(new Date("2007/07/26 19:57 GMT"));</script><noscript>2007/07/26 19:57 GMT</noscript>)
	
	
	
	[<a href="/web/20090523155028/http://ja.doukaku.org/lang/commonlisp/">
	  Common Lisp
	</a>]
	
	
	
	&nbsp;

<span class="rating">評価<span style="background-color: #efffef;">1/1=1.00</span></span>
  </p>
  <div class="comment_content">
	<div class="comment_body">
	  AllegroCL の base64, mime パッケージをつかってます。テンプレートやデータ形式は問題のものを使ってます。
	</div>
	
	
	
    <div class="compact">
      <table><tr><td class="linenos"><pre> 1
